<section xml:id="_depresión_en_adolescentes">
<title>Depresión en adolescentes</title>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<simpara>Escitalopram <footnote><simpara>EMSLIE, Graham J., et al. Escitalopram in the treatment of adolescent depression: a randomized placebo-controlled multisite trial. Journal of the American Academy of Child &amp; Adolescent Psychiatry, 2009, vol. 48, no 7, p. 721-729.</simpara></footnote>] <footnote><simpara>FINDLING, Robert L.; ROBB, Adelaide; BOSE, Anjana. Escitalopram in the treatment of adolescent depression: a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled extension trial. Journal of child and adolescent psychopharmacology, 2013, vol. 23, no 7, p. 468-480.</simpara></footnote></simpara>
